  <brief_title>Phase II Study of Erlotinib With Concurrent Radiotherapy in Unresectable NSCLC With Activating Mutation of EGFR in Exon 19 or 21</brief_title>
  <acronym>RECEL</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Open-label, Phase II Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Erlotinib Versus Etoposide Plus Cisplatin With Concurrent Radiotherapy in Unresectable Stage III Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) With Activating Mutation of Epidermal Growth Factor Receptor (EGFR) in Exon 19 or 21</official_title>
