  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Erlotinib with concurrent radiotherapy has superior efficacy and comparable safety profile in
      unresectable stage III non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) patients with activating mutation
      of epidermal growth factor receptor (EGFR) in exon 19 or 21 versus etoposide plus cis-platin
      with concurrent radiotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
